  <brief_title>Examination Chair for Hip Internal Rotation Range of Motion Measurement</brief_title>
  <acronym>HIRROM</acronym>
  <official_title>Validation of a Test Protocol for Measuring the Hip Internal Rotation Range of Motion Using a Newly Developed Examination Chair</official_title>
  <sponsors>
